733
00:29:17,880 --> 00:29:18,830
I was wrong.

734
00:29:19,720 --> 00:29:20,240
My brother.

735
00:29:20,240 --> 00:29:22,000
I really have been foolish.

736
00:29:26,720 --> 00:29:28,180
Political Commissar Wen,

737
00:29:28,550 --> 00:29:30,150
